</font><P><P><i></i></TD></TR><TR BGCOLOR=#dcdeed><TD NOWRAP width=20% valign=top align=left><B><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=2><A HREF=http://pub6.ezboard.com/uhammyr.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Hammyr</A></FONT></B><BR><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1>Registered User</FONT><BR><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1>(</FONT><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1 COLOR=#333333>7/17/00</FONT> <FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1 COLOR=#333333>5:45:38 pm</FONT><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1>)<BR></FONT></TD><TD VALIGN=TOP ALIGN=LEFT><B><FONT SIZE=2 FACE="Verdana,Arial">.</font></B><HR><FONT SIZE=2 FACE="Verdana,Arial">You can tell defense is not king in this game because even when you increase your defense by a ton, the chance you will get hit does not go down by anything, maybe 1%.  I say resistances are king in this game because almost everything at higher lvl's is enhanced and hits you with some sort of magic.  </font><P><P><i></i></TD></TR><TR BGCOLOR=#989dca><TD NOWRAP width=20% valign=top align=left><B><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=2><A HREF=http://pub6.ezboard.com/ukasea.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Kasea</A></FONT></B><BR><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1>Registered User</FONT><BR><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1>(</FONT><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1 COLOR=#333333>7/17/00</FONT> <FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1 COLOR=#333333>8:41:48 pm</FONT><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1>)<BR></FONT></TD><TD VALIGN=TOP ALIGN=LEFT><B><FONT SIZE=2 FACE="Verdana,Arial">Re: .</font></B><HR><FONT SIZE=2 FACE="Verdana,Arial">I really hate those dam stag beetles that spew lightning when you hit them.  grrrr<br>
